bugzilla-ci adds code inspection functionality to Bugzilla + ScmBug + viewvc

Since v0.12 the code is open source under GNU General Public License v0.3.

The script should be installed in Firefox using Greasemonkey. Chrome support is planned for future releases.

Features:
Merge all commits for single file into one entry
Allow to post code inspection comments with different severity
Collapse unneeded comments
and some more...
